</P>
<P>
 Gossom, Chin Myong, 64, of San Fernando, homemaker. Forest Lawn Mortuary, 
Hollywood Hills. Hoyle, Constance Mary, 65, of Reseda, shipping clerk for Olga 
Warner Co. Forest Lawn Mortuary, Hollywood Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Lingle, William H., 72, of West Hills, retired engineer for Hughes Aircraft. 
Bastian & Perrott Mortuary, Northridge.  
</P>
<P>
 Milstein, Hyman, 81, of Sherman Oaks, retired garment union representative. 
San Fernando Mortuary, San Fernando.  
</P>
<P>
 Neumeier, Frances R., 85, of Glendale, retired teacher and nurse for Glendale 
Unified School District. Woods Glendale Mortuary, Glendale.  
</P>
<P>
 Plumb, Ernest W., 82, of Glendale, retired liquor store owner. Forest Lawn 
Mortuary, Glendale. 
</P>
<P>
