<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Clarification -- A story about writer Gary Paulsen in Sunday's Life & Style 
contained several editing errors.Paulsen's novel "Dogsong" was published in 
1985 and he ran his second Iditarod race in 1985. "Winterdance" was published 
by Harcourt Brace and "Father Water, Mother Woods" by Delacorte. Also, the 
story may have given the impression that Paulsen's wife accompanied him in the 
Iditarod races; she did not. 
</P>
